    def delete_rest(self, direction):

        self.tab_deque = None

        if direction > 0:

            self.copy = self.line[self.pos:]

            self.line = self.line[:self.pos]

        else:

            self.copy = self.line[:self.pos]

            self.line = self.line[self.pos:]

            self.pos = 0

        self.on_line_change()
